#. type: Title =
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Electron Tube"
msgstr "电子管"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:4
msgid ""
"Electron tubes may be placed inside factory controllers, in which they "
"function as boolean logic operators for redstone connections. When placed, "
"they are referred to as \"logical tubes\"."
msgstr ""
"电子管可以放入工厂控制台，并作为红石连接的布尔逻辑运算组件。放入后，电子管被"
"称为“逻辑管”。"

#. type: Block title
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "Logical tubes in each of the 4 modes, powered on and off"
msgstr "四种模式下的逻辑管，包括未充能和已充能的"

#. type: Block title
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "A logical OR operator taking inputs from xref:factory-gauge.adoc[factory gauges] and outputs to a xref:redstone-link.adoc[redstone link]"
msgstr ""
"从xref:factory-gauge.adoc[工厂仪表]接收输入并向xref:redstone-link.adoc[无线红"
"石信号终端]输出的逻辑或组件"

#. type: Title ==
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Logical Operators"
msgstr "逻辑运算符"

#. type: #logical-operators
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:15
msgid ""
"Each logical tube may be connected with 0 or more redstone inputs, and "
"outputs a redstone signal according the rules of a logical operator, "
"determined by its mode."
msgstr ""
"每个逻辑管都可连接零个或多个红石输入，并根据当前逻辑运算模式决定是否输出红石"
"信号。"

#. type: #logical-operators
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:17
msgid "The available modes are:"
msgstr "支持的模式有："

#. type: Labeled list
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "OR"
msgstr "或"

#. type: #logical-operators
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:20
msgid ""
"Output on when any connected input is on. Otherwise output off. When "
"unconnected, output off."
msgstr "任意一个输入为真时输出真，否则输出假。没有连接时输出假。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "AND"
msgstr "和"

#. type: #logical-operators
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:23
msgid ""
"Output on when all connected inputs are on. Otherwise output off. When "
"unconnected, output on."
msgstr "所有输入均为真时输出真，否则输出假。没有连接时输出真。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "NOR"
msgstr "或非"

#. type: #logical-operators
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:26
msgid "Inverse of OR."
msgstr "逻辑或的反相结果。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "NAND"
msgstr "与非"

#. type: #logical-operators
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:29
msgid "Inverse of AND."
msgstr "逻辑与的反相结果。"

#. type: Title ==
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:31 ../src/redstone-link.adoc:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "配置"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:34
msgid "Clicking on the placed logical tube opens its settings screen."
msgstr "点击已放置的逻辑管可打开设置界面。"

#. type: Block title
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Logical tube settings"
msgstr "逻辑管设置界面"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:40
msgid ""
"❶ Inputs:: Displays the components connected as inputs to this tube. Click a "
"component to switch it to an output, shift-click to disconnect."
msgstr ""
"❶ 输入:: 显示作为此逻辑管输入的组件。点击组件可将其切换为输出，按住 Shift 点"
"击以断开连接。"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:43
msgid "❷ Operator:: Displays the currently selected operator."
msgstr "❷ 运算符:: 显示当前选择的逻辑运算。"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:46
msgid ""
"❸ Outputs:: Displays the components connected as outputs to this tube. Click "
"a component to switch it to an input, shift-click to disconnect."
msgstr ""
"❸ 输出:: 显示作为此逻辑管输出的组件。点击组件可将其切换为输入，按住 Shift 点"
"击以断开连接。"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:49
msgid ""
"❹ Relocate button:: Click to move the location of this logical tube on the "
"virtual board."
msgstr "❹ 移动组件:: 点击以在虚拟面板上移动逻辑管。"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:52
msgid ""
"❺ Add connection button:: Click to connect to other components via redstone."
msgstr "❺ 新建连接按钮:: 点击通过红石连接到其他组件。"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:55
msgid "❻ Mode switch:: Click to switch between OR, AND, NOR, NAND modes."
msgstr "❻ 模式切换:: 在逻辑或、与、或非、与非之间切换。"

#. type: #configuration
#: ../src/electron-tube.adoc:57
msgid "❼ Confirm button:: Click to confirm settings and close this screen."
msgstr "❼ 确认按钮:: 保存设置并关闭界面。"
